entries.femaleVariant: Isn't that what growing up's all about?
You mean looking like a zombie and being obsessed with guns?
We used to be able to talk about everything together... now it's just Militech this, Militech that.
I miss the stuff we used to  talk about... and you, too.
I'm part of something bigger now. Before Militech I used to be a nobody... like you.
You should find a job. Clearly you've got too much free time on your hands.
